🔗 Logical Operators

| Operator | Name        | Example           | Output  |
| -------- | ----------- | ----------------- | ------- |
| `&&`     | Logical AND | `true && false`   | `false` |
| `\|\|`   | Logical OR  | `true \|\| false` | `true`  |
| `!`      | Logical NOT | `!false`          | `true`  |
